# Internal context / planning that lives alongside the repo but isn't
# part of the public artefact. The brief docs and meeting transcripts
# under `brief/` and `context/` are working materials, not shipping
# code — keep them out of the public repo. (Move them back in or open
# a private repo if you want them version-controlled.)
brief/
context/
KICKOFF.md

# Local agent simulation artefacts (bulky JSON run dumps stay local); the
# curated markdown deliverables under reports/ (audit closure, follow-ups,
# blocked log, goal-run reports) ARE tracked.
reports/*.json
*.log
.claude/

# Firebase Hosting build intermediates — generated during `firebase deploy`
.firebase/

# Style-exploration outputs from `node scripts/explore-styles.mjs`.
# Useful locally for picking a style; not part of the shipping artefact.
public/img/explore/


# Playwright e2e artifacts
test-results/
playwright-report/
